      "message": "Patch Set 6: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nArgh, patch #5 had just passed testing 20 minutes earlier, but the patch was then resubmitted...\n\nAurelien, your updated patch reverted fixes that Johann had made in his latest update. Please resubmit with those fixes. \n\nI guess this is due to you pushing a patch on top of Johann's patch?  In that case you should check out the branch that this patch is on, and avoid rebasing the branch unless you intentionally want to resubmit the patches.",
